title: BigFish Games - Liong The Lost Amulets - New Hidden Object Mahjo
description:
Liong: The Lost Amulets truly is a game unlike 
any other.
It's a combination of hidden object games 
and tile-matching puzzles and 
also has a variety of mini games. 
Along your journey you'll visit 
hundreds of unique locations and collect 
power-up pearls. Reveal the 
magic spells and restore the sparkling 
gems of the magical amulets.
Featuring:
2 game modes
100+ levels of game play
Challenging Mini-Games and Hidden Object fun
System Requirements:
OS: Windows Vista, Windows XP, Windows 98, Windows 2000
Processor: 1000 Mhz Intel Pentium
Memory: 512 MB RAM
Disk Space: 39 MB
DirectX: 7.0
